# Re-include project files that a parent (LAB) .gitignore excludes by broad
# pattern (.env.*, *.png, package-lock.json). These are required, committed
# artifacts for this deployable web project — and contain no secrets.
!.env.example
!package-lock.json
!public/*.png
!src/app/*.png
!src/app/**/*.png
